Mail Template for a Sandbox Promotion Vote

 This templates contains most of the data developers expect to do validate a vote.\
 Replace all UPPER_CASE_TERMS with its equivalent value.
 You're free to add or skip sections, just see this as a good starting point.

*---------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Subject | [VOTE] Promote PROJECT_NAME out of the Sandbox
*---------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
| To      | dev@mojo.codehaus.org
*---------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Hi,

I'd like to promote the PROJECT_NAME out of the Sandbox

PROJECT_DESCRIPTION

Site:
PROJECT_URL

SCM Tag:
PROJECT_SCM_URL

ADDITIONAL_INFORMATION

 [ ] +1
 [ ] +0
 [ ] -1

The vote is open for 72 hours and will succeed by lazy consensus.



Regards / Cheers / Thanks /

YOUR_NAME
